<div id="review_3415364341" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3415364341" />
    <a title="Luís" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/117399210-lu-s"><img alt="Luís" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1620236159p2/117399210.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3415364341?book_show_action=true">Jun 28, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Luís" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Luís" href="/user/show/117399210-lu-s">Luís</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Mass Market Paperback 9782253004011" href="/book/show/22017690-les-liaisons-dangereuses">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117399210-lu-s?shelf=classics">classics</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117399210-lu-s?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117399210-lu-s?shelf=historical-fiction">historical-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117399210-lu-s?shelf=france-belgium-swiss">france-belgium-swiss</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117399210-lu-s?shelf=romance">romance</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3415364341" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1398069841941705318">Subtle.<br/>A clinical study of libertines, libertinism and vice-like virtue. A reflection served by a sumptuous text and an absolutely superb language.<br/>A lot of subtlety in the text&apos;s nuances makes this prose a peak in the profusion of details and intensity.<br/>The era is strongly felt, and its atmosphere literally radiates.<br/>Come to think of it; it is above all an essay on human nature ... games ... passion ... cunning and jousting.<br/>By dint of simulating war, we end up waging it.<br/>By dint of manipulating and</span>
  <span id="freeText1398069841941705318" style="display:none">Subtle.<br />A clinical study of libertines, libertinism and vice-like virtue. A reflection served by a sumptuous text and an absolutely superb language.<br />A lot of subtlety in the text's nuances makes this prose a peak in the profusion of details and intensity.<br />The era is strongly felt, and its atmosphere literally radiates.<br />Come to think of it; it is above all an essay on human nature ... games ... passion ... cunning and jousting.<br />By dint of simulating war, we end up waging it.<br />By dint of manipulating and calculating we dehumanize the object of our attention and affection, while we reach ourselves to the same extent?<br />Libertinism is less promoted and weighed in this text than human nature examined. While innocence and virtue are no more respectable in themselves than vice, because they appear as a weakness and an almost maladjustment and ultimately as an obstacle to happiness, balance and reason.<br />What Laclos hoped to demonstrate in my humble opinion and among others, is that only rigour and moderation coupled with will and discernment lead anywhere.<br />This novel is a great moment of French language and civilization.<br />A sort of great exquisite century of subtleties, requirements and breadth.<br />Each sentence is a delight of rhythm, intensity and calculation.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1398069841941705318" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


